name: DOOM Ultimate Action Figure
description:
The Ultimate DOOM. A crossover of the ALL CAPS one with the infamous Demon Slayer. It’s DOOMSDAY FOREVER!!  

Card is made of Mondo’s Doom poster, original art by Gabz. MF DOOM’s art print, original art by Sleepy Fox & a Wikipedia stock image of the BFG 9000.

Figure is made of McFarlane Toys Doom Slayer figure, customized Super 7’s Kawhi Leonard Reaction figure & customized MF DOOM mask action figure. 

The BFG 9000 is made from a Wikipedia stock image.
